NAME
	this_race - returns a users race_object

SYNOPSIS
	object this_race()

DESCRIPTION
	If a users race_object is found return that object, or else
	return the object that called this function.

RETURN VALUE
	A race object, or else the function which called this_race.

EXAMPLES
	object p;
	p = this_race();
	write("Language: " + p->query_language() + "\n");

